4.	Pinto, Isabel. «Intermediality and Cultural Assessment: A review of Digital Humanities and the Study of Intermediality in Comparative Cultural Studies, edited by Steven Tötösy de Zepetnek. Purdue Scholarly Publishing Services, 2013, 375 pp.». DHQ: Digital Humanities Quarterly, 2015, http://digitalhumanities.org:8081/dhq/vol/9/3/000193/000193.html

