7.	Hassapopoulou, Marina. «From Distracted to Distributed Attention: Expanded Learning through Social Media, Augmented Reality, Remixing, and Activist Geocaching». Digital Humanities Quarterly, vol. 012, n.o 2, septiembre de 2018, http://digitalhumanities.org:8081/dhq/vol/12/2/000386/000386.html.

8.	VandeCreek, Drew. «Webs of Significance: The Abraham Lincoln Historical Digitization Project, New Technology, and the Democratization of History». Digital Humanities Quarterly, vol. 001, n.o 1, abril de 2007, http://digitalhumanities.org:8081/dhq/vol/1/1/000003/000003.html.

9.	Fyfe, Paul. «Digital Pedagogy Unplugged». Digital Humanities Quarterly, vol. 005, n.o 3, junio de 2011, http://digitalhumanities.org:8081/dhq/vol/5/3/000106/000106.html.

